        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Rhode Island Fishermen's Fairness Act of 202</b><strong>1</strong></p> <p>This bill adds Rhode Island to the Mid-Atlantic Fishery Management Council and increases council membership from 21 to 23 members. The council is not given authority over the fisheries in the Atlantic Ocean seaward of Rhode Island.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
